quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,133,"Dájúdájú (Ànábì) Lūt wà nínú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́."
  37,134,"(Ẹ rántí) nígbà tí A gba òun àti gbogbo àwọn ará ilé rẹ̀ là."
  37,135,"Àyàfi arúgbóbìnrin kan tí ó wà nínú àwọn tó ṣẹ́ kù lẹ́yìn (láààrin àwọn tí A parẹ́).{1}.",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah aṣ-Ṣu‘arọ̄’; 26:171.
  40,76,"Ẹ wọ àwọn ẹnu ọ̀na iná Jahanamọ; olùṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú rẹ̀. Ó sì burú ní ibùgbé fún àwọn onígbèéraga."
  40,77,"Nítorí náà, ṣe sùúrù. Dájúdájú àdéhùn Allāhu ni òdodo. Ó ṣeé ṣe kí A fi apá kan èyí tí A ṣe ní ìlérí fún wọn hàn ọ́ tàbí kí A ti gba ẹ̀mí rẹ (ṣíwájú àsìkò náà). Ọ̀dọ̀ Wa kúkú ni wọ́n máa dá wọn padà sí."
  40,78,"Àti pé A kúkú ti rán àwọn Òjísẹ́ níṣẹ́ ṣíwájú rẹ. Àwọn tí A sọ ìtàn wọn fún ọ wà nínú wọn. Àwọn tí A kò sọ ìtàn wọn fún ọ wà nínú wọn. Àti pé kò tọ́ fún Òjísẹ́ kan láti mú àmì kan wá àyàfi pẹ̀lú ìyọ̀ǹda Allāhu. Nígbà tí àṣẹ Allāhu bá sì dé, A máa fi òdodo dájọ́. Àwọn òpùrọ́ sì máa ṣòfò dànù níbẹ̀ yẹn.{1}.",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah ar-Ra‘d; 13:38 lórí ìtúmọ̀ “àmì”.
  42,40,"Ẹ̀san aburú sì ni aburú bí irú rẹ̀.{1} Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá sì ṣàmójúkúrò, tí ó tún ṣàtúnṣe, ẹ̀san rẹ̀ wà lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu. Dájúdájú (Allāhu) kò nífẹ̀ẹ́ àwọn alábòsí..",footnotes:1:Kíyè sí i, gbólóhùn yìí “Ẹ̀san aburú sì ni aburú bí irú rẹ̀.” kò tako sūrah Fussilat; 41:31. Ìdí ni pé, gbígba ẹ̀san lára alábòsí tàbí gbígba ààrọ̀ kò sọ pé mùsùlùmí kò ní ẹ̀mí àforíjìn, àmọ́ ó lè má nìí agbára láti ṣàmójú kúrò fún alábòsí náà.
  42,41,"Dájúdájú ẹni tí ó bá sì gbẹ̀san lẹ́yìn tí wọ́n ṣe àbòsí sí i, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn (tí wọ́n ṣàbòsí sí), kò sí ìbáwí kan kan fún wọn."
  42,42,"Àwọn tí ìbáwí wà fún ni àwọn tó ń ṣàbòsí sí àwọn ènìyàn, tí wọ́n tún ń tayọ ẹnu-ààlà lórí ilẹ̀ láì lẹ́tọ̀ọ́. Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro wà fún."
  43,22,"Rárá. Wọ́n wí pé: “Dájúdájú àwa bá àwọn bàbá wa lórí ẹ̀sìn kan. Dájúdájú àwa sì ni olùmọ̀nà lórí orípa wọn.”{1}.",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo āyah 37 àti 38 níwájú.
  43,23,"Bákan náà, Àwa kò rán olùkìlọ̀ kan sí ìlú kan ṣíwájú rẹ, àyàfi kí àwọn onígbẹdẹmukẹ ìlú náà wí pé: “Dájúdájú àwa bá àwọn bàbá wa lórí ẹ̀sìn kan. Dájúdájú àwa sì ni olùtẹ̀lé wọn lórí orípa wọn.”"
  43,24,"(Olùkìlọ̀) sì sọ pé: “Ǹjẹ́ èmi kò ti mú wá fún yín ohun tí ó jẹ́ ìmọ̀nà jùlọ sí ohun tí ẹ bá àwọn bàbá yín lórí rẹ̀?” Wọ́n wí pé: “Dájúdájú àwa jẹ́ aláìgbàgbọ́ nínú ohun tí wọ́n fi ran yín níṣẹ́.”"
  44,7,"Olúwa àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ àti ohunkóhun tí ń bẹ láààrin méjèèjì tí ẹ̀yin bá jẹ́ alámọ̀dájú."
  44,8,"Kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí ẹ gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Òun. Ó ń sọ ẹ̀dá di alààyè. Ó sì ń sọ ẹ̀dá di òkú. Olúwa yín àti Olúwa àwọn bàbá yín, àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́."
  44,9,"Síbẹ̀, wọ́n sì wà nínú iyèméjì, tí wọ́n ń ṣeré."